        <t>&lt;p&gt;This document discusses the need for delegation of the IP6.ARPA DNS zone, and specifies a plan for the technical operation thereof.  This document specifies an Internet Best Current Practices for the Internet Community, and requests discussion and suggestions for improvements.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
